<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>当请求接口不返回数据时，封装后响应体传递的</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> JSON </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>数据中</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> data </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>的值就会显示为</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> null</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>，整体上看起来并不协调，我们可以对</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> data </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>的空值进行处理，转化为空符串</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>Jackson2ObjectMapperBuilder</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>来建一个</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>ObjectMapper</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>用于获取当前</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>ObjectMapper</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>实例的序列化对象，然后将序列化时为</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> null </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>值实例化一个新的</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>JsonSerializer</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>类用于写入为空字符串</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:13.5pt'><span
style='font-weight:bold'>类型空处理</span></p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>虽然将</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> null </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>值显示为空字符串协调了响应体，但是仍然没解决数据应该根据类型显示的问题。正常情况下，我们应该能够根据</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> JSON </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>中的数据格式大致判断出属性的数据类型，而不是统一处理为空字符。</span></li>
